Title: The Witch Beneath the Sea
Writer: Austin Green, Anita Manville, Monica Sulistrowski, Zygmunt Sulistrowski (story), Zygmunt Sulistrowski
Actors: John Sutton, Richard Olizar, Gina Albert, Eugenio Carlos
Plot: A novelist comes under the spell of a beautiful woman who is rumored to be a legendary Amazon who lures men to their doom.
